    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A substance that causes the union of separate materials or particles into a group or mass; includes glue or other adhesive that serves this function in making aqueous paint, pastels, and ink for drawing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sustancia que permite la unión de materiales o partículas separadas para formar un grupo o masa. Incluye la cola y otros adhesivos que cumplen esta función en la fabricación de pinturas acuosas, pasteles y tinta de dibujo.
</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Een substantie die individuele materialen of deeltjes tot één groep of massa verenigt; ook lijm of andere hechtmiddelen die voor dit doel worden toegevoegd aan verf op waterbasis, pastel en Oost-Indische inkt.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>一種可引起個別材料或粒子結合為一群或一團的材料；包括黏著劑或其他具備此項功能的膠黏劑，可用來製作水溶性的繪畫顏料、粉蠟筆和素描用的墨水。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
